<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
      Verify Your Account - OLA LSSU
    </title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; background-color: #f9fafb;"
  >
    <div
      style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);"
    >

      <!-- Header -->
      <div
        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0bae53 0%, #0c8040 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 32px; text-align: center;"
      >
        <div
          style="display: inline-block; width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: #10b981; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; line-height: 60px; font-size: 30px; font-weight: bold;"
        >
          ‚úì
        </div>
        <h1 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff;">
          Verify Your Account
        </h1>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; opacity: 0.9;">
          Complete your registration with OLA LSSU
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div style="padding: 32px;">
        <div style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #374151;">
          Hello there!
        </div>

        <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 30px;">
          Welcome to OLA LSSU! To complete your account setup and ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address using the verification code below.
        </div>

        <!-- OTP Code Section -->
        <div
          style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; border: 2px dashed #d1d5db;"
        >
          <div style="font-size: 16px; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 500;">
            Your verification code:
          </div>
          <div
            style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #0bae53; letter-spacing: 8px; margin: 16px 0; font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 16px 24px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; display: inline-block;"
          >
            {{ otp }}
          </div>
          <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 16px; font-weight: 500;">
            ‚è∞ This code expires in 10 minutes
          </div>
        </div>

        {{ url }}
        <!-- Verification Button -->
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
          <!--[if mso]>
              <v:roundrect xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" href="{{ verificationUrl }}" style="height:50px;v-text-anchor:middle;width:280px;" arcsize="20%" stroke="f" fillcolor="#0bae53">
                <w:anchorlock/>
                <center>
          <![endif]-->
          <a
            href="{{ url }}"
            style="background-color: #0bae53; color: #ffffff; padding: 16px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block; min-width: 200px; text-align: center; border: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(11, 174, 83, 0.3); transition: all 0.3s ease;"
          >
            üöÄ Verify My Email Address
              </a>
          <!--[if mso]>
                </center>
              </v:roundrect>
          <![endif]-->
        </div>

        <!-- Security Notice -->
        <div
          style="background-color: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;"
        >
          <h4 style="color: #b45309; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0;">
            üîí Security Notice
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #78350f; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
            <strong>Keep this code confidential!</strong>This verification code is for your use only‚Äînever share it with anyone. If you didn't request it, please ignore this email; your account will remain secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #6b7280;">
          Having trouble with verification? Click the button above to verify your email automatically, or contact our support team for help.<br />
          Thank you for joining OLA LSSU‚Äîwe're excited to welcome you to the community!
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div
        style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"
      >
        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
          ¬© OLA LSSU. All rights reserved.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
          This is an automated message. For support, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@olalssu.com" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;">support
            @olalssu.com
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fallback for older email clients -->
    <!--[if mso]>
    <style>
    .otp-code { font-size: 32px !important; letter-spacing: 4px !important; }
    </style>
    <![endif]-->
  </body>
</html>
